[[File:Volke, Igor.IMG 1814.JPG|thumb|Igor Volke in 2014]]
'''Igor Volke''' (born 19 January 1950 in [[Jõgeva]], [[Estonia]]) is an Estonian [[ufologist]] and researcher of environmental anomalies.<ref name=leivak>{{cite web |url=http://www.postimees.ee/1299000/igor-volke-ja-avanev-maailm |title=Igor Volke ja avanev maailm |publisher=''[[Postimees]]'' |author=Leivak, Verni |date=13 July 2013 |language=Estonian}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.postimees.ee/2467371/tundmatud-joud-loopisid-korteris-esemeid-tuhalaanes-poles-rahvamaja |title=Tundmatud jõud loopisid korteris esemeid |publisher=''Postimees'' |author=Aotäht, Aivar |date=10 January 1996 |language=Estonian}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |url=https://books.google.ee/books?id=de7OBAAAQBAJ&pg=PT272&lpg=PT272&dq=%22igor+volke%22&source=bl&ots=Uluj_10ydN&sig=Sdpc_Ri-Pc39dYqbyQVh8__QoQc&hl=en&sa=X&ei=Qdo8VfOVPMGysgGrt4HoCQ&ved=0CHMQ6AEwEg#v=onepage&q=%22igor%20volke%22&f=false |title=Vernacular Religion in Everyday Life: Expressions of Belief |last1=Bowman |first1=Marion |last2=Valk |first2=Ulo |publisher=[[Routledge]] |year=2014 |isbn=9781317543534}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://r2.err.ee/v/hallokosmos/uudised/ca31c0b8-f728-452c-9010-abe918a29797 |title="Hallo, Kosmos!" 180: "Solarise needus" II osa: Saale Kareda, Igor Volke + Port, Olesk, Veskimees, Eelmaa |publisher=[[Raadio 2]]/[[Eesti Rahvusringhääling|ERR]] |date=6 June 2014 |language=Estonian}}</ref>

In 1985 he founded the organization [[AKRAK]] for the purpose of collecting reports of anomalous environmental phenomena.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.virumaateataja.ee/291206/esileht/15035314.php |title=Igor Volke on näinud kolme ufot |publisher=''[[Virumaa Teataja]]'' |date=29 December 2006 |author=Klaas, Eva }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://novaator.err.ee/v/yhiskond/d8dcfddb-a463-49cc-95ee-7bc4515efc95 |title=Folklorist ja ufoloog selgitavad, miks ufod jätkuvalt inimesi huvitavad |publisher=[[Novaator]]/ERR |date=28 January 2015 |language=Estonian }}</ref>

Volke graduated from [[Tallinn School No. 21]] in 1968, and [[Tallinn University of Technology]] in 1972. He worked in the Tallinn fire department from 1970–2000, and since 2000 works at the [[National Library of Estonia]] as an occupational safety specialist.<ref name=leivak /> He is married and has three children.<ref name=leivak />

==Works==
* {{cite book |title=UFO-raamat |last=Volke |first=Igor |publisher=[[Perioodika]] |year=1991 |isbn=9785797904045 |pages=95}}
* {{cite book |title=Ufopäevikud |last=Volke |first=Igor |publisher=[[BNS Kirjastus]] |year=1998 | isbn=9789985883099 |pages=301}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://epl.delfi.ee/news/eesti/volke-ullitasufopaevikud?id=50758127 |title=Volke üllitas"Ufopäevikud" |publisher=''[[Eesti Päevaleht]]'' |date=9 July 1998 |language=Estonian}}</ref>

The book ''Ufopäevikud'' (''UFO Diaries'') consists mostly of UFO reports from around the world, starting with the 1940s, with special sections at the end for reports from Estonia and [[Finland]].

