'''I Putu Gede Juni Antara''' (born 7 June 1995)<ref name=goal>[http://www.goal.com/en-us/people/indonesia/110289/putu-gede-juni-antara Putu Gede Juni Antara] at goal.com. Retrieved on 7 December 2015.</ref> is an Indonesian footballer who currently plays for [[Bhayangkara F.C.|Bhayangkara]] as a right-back. He is also a [[Brigadier#Indonesia|Second Police Brigadier]] in the [[Indonesian National Police]].
== Club career == === Persebaya Surabaya === On 11 November 2014, Putu Gede signed a four-year contract with [[Persebaya Surabaya]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Tujuh Pemain Timnas U-19 Dikontrak Persebaya 4 Tahun|url=http://bola.metrotvnews.com/read/2014/11/11/317120/tujuh-pemain-timnas-u-19-dikontrak-persebaya-4-tahun|accessdate=28 November 2014|language=Indonesian}}</ref> He made his debut on 5 April 2015 as starting line-up, which ended 1–0 victory against [[Mitra Kukar]] at [[Gelora Bung Tomo Stadium]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Laporan Pertandingan: Persebaya Surabaya 1–0 Mitra Kukar|url=http://www.goal.com/id-ID/match/persebaya-surabaya-vs-mitra-kukar/2016887/report?ICID=MP_MS_5|accessdate=5 April 2015|work=goal.com|last = Afroni| first = Donny|language=Indonesian}}</ref>
== Personal life == Putu Gede Juni Antara is the only son of [[Bali]]nese parents and is a practicing [[Hinduism|Hindu]]. He is considered very sociable and friendly by his teammates with multiple social media accounts.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://renytariga.blogspot.com/2013/11/biodata-dan-fakta-putu-gede-juni-antara.html |work=All About Sports |title=biodata dan fakta Putu Gede juni antara pemain timnas u-19 |date=2 November 2013 |accessdate=1 October 2015 |language=Indonesian}}</ref>
== International career == He made his international debut for senior team on 21 March 2017, against [[Myanmar national football team|Myanmar]].<ref>http://www.pikiran-rakyat.com/olah-raga/2017/03/21/susunan-pemain-timnas-indonesia-u-23-vs-myanmar-396848</ref>
